      "chain_id": "chain-02",
      "chain_name": "Subtle State Confusion Pivot To Ssrf",
      "attack_scenario": "Attacker combines a low-visibility entry point with stored or derived application state, then pivots to a higher-impact sink that is reachable only after following the cross-file flow.",
